data.description: Discover luxury living at 4034 Willowmere Trace in Kennesaw, GA's sought-after Annandale at Legacy Park.   This stunning 4-bed, 2.5-bath home epitomizes the easy-care lifestyle and a sense of community!   2-story hardwood foyer entry provides a timeless entry mixed with a ray of natural light.   Main Floor: Office or Study with French door privacy; Formal Dining Room, Eat In Kitchen overlooking private backyard oasis; Open kitchen concept w/breakfast area flows easily into the cozy family room w/fireplace.   Upper Level: Owner's solace boasts unimaginable space and multiple sitting areas; a luxury bath w/double vanity, soaking tub, and separate glass shower.  Three spacious secondary bedrooms w/shared bath; laundry room.   Enjoy proximity to town, schools, and highways, plus community amenities like pools, tennis courts, and playgrounds.   Will You Be the New Owner?   Request "ALL" Showings via ShowingTime; Submit "all" via Offer Manager within GAMLS ShowingTime.
